text: Macropholidus annectens, Parker's pholiodobolus , is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Ecuador. ==References== Category:Macropholidus Category:Reptiles of Ecuador Category:Endemic fauna of Ecuador Category:Reptiles described in 1930 Category:Taxa named by Hampton Wildman Parker
